title: Week 13 Recap, MVP Keenum, Giants Mess, Jimmy G Impresses (Football 12/04)
description:
Will Brinson, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora recap Week 13 in the NFL. Will and Jason discuss the fraudulent Titans (1:45), Case Keenum's case for MVP (8:30), Jimmy G's starting debut for San Francisco (15:15), and the state of the AFC West (20:05). Then, Nick and Pete link up with Will to cover the Saints solidifying themselves as the class of the NFC South (26:15), the Browns potential moving forward(42:30), and the craziness that is coming with coaching turnover in the league (50:30).
